title: 05 — Light & Dark Rooms
story: regression
author: Sharpee Regression Suite
description: Verify dark room blocks vision, flashlight provides light

---

# Go south to the supply closet without a light
> south
[OK: contains "dark"]

# Can't see anything
> look
[OK: contains "dark"]

# Go back and get the flashlight
> north
[OK: contains "Control Room"]

> take flashlight
[OK: contains "Taken"]

# Flashlight is off — closet still dark
> south
[OK: contains "dark"]

> north
[OK: contains "Control Room"]

# Turn on the flashlight
> switch on flashlight
[OK: contains "on"]

# Now the closet should be lit
> south
[OK: contains "Supply Closet"]
[OK: contains "toolbox"]

# Turn off flashlight — dark again
> switch off flashlight
[OK: contains "off"]

> look
[OK: contains "dark"]
